  <brief_title>Septal - Success Rate and Clinical Outcome of Septal Implant of Ventricular Defibrillation Lead</brief_title>
  <official_title>Evaluation of the Success Rate and the Clinical Evolution of a Ventricular Lead Implanted in the Septum Versus the Right Ventricular Apex.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Boston Scientific Corporation</agency>
      <agency_class>Industry</agency_class>
